WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:24.040
5. The Law of Karma and the Law of Forgiveness

00:26.740 --> 00:34.200
Man receives only that which he gives. The game of life is a game of boomerangs. Man's thoughts,

00:34.360 --> 00:41.260
deeds, and words return to him sooner or later, with astounding accuracy. This is the law of

00:41.260 --> 00:51.320
karma, which is Sanskrit for comeback. Whatsoever a man soweth, that shall he also reap. For example,

00:51.320 --> 00:56.320
a friend told me this story of herself illustrating the law. She said,

00:57.040 --> 01:03.960
I make all my karma on my aunt. Whatever I say to her, someone says to me. I am often

01:03.960 --> 01:10.400
irritable at home when one day said to my aunt who was talking to me during dinner,

01:11.320 --> 01:17.020
no more talk, I wish to eat in peace. The following day I was lunching with a woman

01:17.020 --> 01:21.900
with whom I wished to make a great impression. I was talking animatedly when she said,

01:22.140 --> 01:27.600
no more talk, I wish to eat in peace. My friend is high in consciousness,

01:27.700 --> 01:35.200
so her karma returns much more quickly than to one on the mental plane. The more man knows,

01:35.360 --> 01:40.580
the more he is responsible for, and a person with a knowledge of spiritual law,

01:40.580 --> 01:44.860
which he does not practice, suffers greatly in consequence.

01:46.000 --> 01:53.800
The fear of the Lord, law, is the beginning of wisdom. If we read the word Lord, law,

01:54.340 --> 01:57.200
it will make many passages in the Bible much clearer.

01:58.500 --> 02:07.060
Vengeance is mine, I will repay, saith the Lord, law. It is the law which takes vengeance, not God.

02:07.060 --> 02:15.200
God sees man perfect, created in his own image, imagination, and given power and dominion.

02:16.240 --> 02:22.920
This is the perfect idea of man, registered in divine mind, awaiting man's recognition,

02:23.400 --> 02:29.980
for man can only be what he sees himself to be, and only attain what he sees himself attaining.

02:30.700 --> 02:34.820
Nothing ever happens without an onlooker, is an ancient saying.

02:35.740 --> 02:42.780
Man first sees his failure or success, his joy or sorrow, before it swings into visibility,

02:43.060 --> 02:49.240
from the scenes set in his own imagination. We have observed this in the mother picturing

02:49.240 --> 02:55.680
disease for her child, or a woman seeing success for her husband. Jesus Christ said,

02:55.680 --> 03:01.960
Ye shall know the truth, and the truth shall make you free. So we see freedom,

03:02.160 --> 03:07.760
from all unhappy conditions, comes through knowledge, a knowledge of spiritual law.

03:08.820 --> 03:15.220
Obedience precedes authority, and the law obeys man when he obeys the law.

03:15.800 --> 03:23.020
The law of electricity must be obeyed before it becomes man's servant. When handled ignorantly,

03:23.020 --> 03:31.380
it becomes man's deadly foe, so with the laws of mind. For example, a woman with a strong personal

03:31.380 --> 03:37.280
will, wished she owned a house which belonged to an acquaintance, and she often made mental

03:37.280 --> 03:43.700
pictures of herself living in the house. In the course of time, the man died, and she moved into

03:43.700 --> 03:49.500
the house. Several years afterwards, coming into the knowledge of spiritual law, she said to me,

03:49.500 --> 03:57.280
Do you think I had anything to do with that man's death? I replied, Yes, your desire was so strong,

03:57.540 --> 04:03.620
everything made way for it. But you paid your karmic debt, your husband, whom you loved

04:03.620 --> 04:10.420
devotedly, died soon after, and the house was a white elephant on your hands for many years.

04:11.620 --> 04:15.760
The original owner, however, could not have been affected by her thoughts,

04:15.760 --> 04:22.140
had he been positive in the truth, nor her husband, but they were both under karmic law.

04:22.920 --> 04:26.900
The woman should have said, feeling the great desire for the house,

04:27.880 --> 04:32.760
Infinite intelligence, give me the right house, equally as charming as this,

04:33.200 --> 04:39.160
the house which is mine by divine right. The divine selection would have given perfect

04:39.160 --> 04:45.300
satisfaction, and brought good to all. The divine pattern is the only safe pattern to work by.

04:45.760 --> 04:53.060
Desire is a tremendous force, and must be directed in the right channels, or chaos ensues.

04:54.160 --> 05:01.600
In demonstrating, the most important step is the first step, to ask a right. Man should always

05:01.600 --> 05:08.580
demand only that which is his by divine right. To go back to the illustration, had the woman

05:08.580 --> 05:17.500
taken this attitude. If this house, I desire, is mine, I cannot lose it. If it is not, give me

05:17.500 --> 05:23.800
its equivalent. The man might have decided to move out harmoniously, had it been the divine

05:23.800 --> 05:30.040
selection for her, or another house would have been substituted. Anything forced into manifestation

05:30.040 --> 05:36.140
through personal will is always ill-got, and has ever-bad success.

05:37.740 --> 05:45.660
Man is admonished, my will be done, not thine. And the curious thing is, man always gets just

05:45.660 --> 05:52.080
what he desires, when he does relinquish all personal will, thereby enabling infinite

05:52.080 --> 05:58.340
intelligence to work through him. Stand ye still, and see the salvation of the Lord,

05:58.340 --> 06:05.680
law. For example, a woman came to me in great distress. Her daughter had determined to take

06:05.680 --> 06:12.300
a very hazardous trip, and the mother was filled with fear. She said she had used every argument,

06:12.780 --> 06:18.680
had pointed out the dangers to be encountered, had forbidden her to go, but the daughter became

06:18.680 --> 06:25.120
more and more rebellious and determined. I said to the mother, you are forcing your personal will

06:25.120 --> 06:31.520
upon your daughter, which you have no right to do, and your fear of the trip is only attracting

06:31.520 --> 06:39.920
it, for man attracts what he fears. I added, let go and take your mental hands off,

06:40.360 --> 06:48.900
put it in God's hands, and use this statement. I put this situation in the hands of infinite

06:48.900 --> 06:56.080
love and wisdom. If this trip is the divine plan, I bless it and no longer resist,

06:56.560 --> 07:02.920
but if it is not divinely planned, I give thanks that it is now dissolved and dissipated.

07:04.340 --> 07:09.520
A day or two after that, her daughter said to her, mother, I have given up the trip.

07:10.180 --> 07:17.220
And the situation returned to its native nothingness. It is learning to stand still,

07:17.220 --> 07:23.780
which seems so difficult for man. I will deal more fully with this law in the chapter on

07:23.780 --> 07:30.360
non-resistance. I will give another example of sowing and reaping which came in the most

07:30.360 --> 07:36.780
curious way. A woman came to me saying she had received a counterfeit twenty dollar bill

07:36.780 --> 07:44.040
given to her at the bank. She was much disturbed for, she said, the people at the bank will never

07:44.040 --> 07:51.640
acknowledge their mistake. I replied, let us analyze the situation and find out why you

07:51.640 --> 07:58.880
attracted it. She thought a few moments and exclaimed, I know it. I sent a friend a lot of

07:58.880 --> 08:06.120
stage money just for a joke. So the law had sent her some stage money, for it doesn't know anything

08:06.120 --> 08:14.500
about jokes. I said, now we will call on the law of forgiveness and neutralize the situation.

08:15.940 --> 08:20.640
Christianity is founded upon the law of forgiveness. Christ has redeemed us from

08:20.640 --> 08:26.420
the curse of the karmic law, and the Christ within each man is his redeemer and salvation

08:26.420 --> 08:34.320
from all inharmonious conditions. So I said, infinite spirit, we call on the law of forgiveness

08:34.320 --> 08:41.340
and give thanks that she is under grace and not under law and cannot lose this twenty dollars

08:41.340 --> 08:49.180
which is hers by divine right. Now I said, go back to the bank and tell them fearlessly

08:49.180 --> 08:56.940
that it was given you there by mistake. She obeyed and, to her surprise, they apologized

08:56.940 --> 09:03.420
and gave her another bill treating her most courteously. So knowledge of the law gives man

09:03.420 --> 09:09.980
power to rub out his mistakes. Man cannot force the external to be what he is not.

09:10.520 --> 09:14.540
If he desires riches, he must be rich first in consciousness.

09:16.400 --> 09:22.980
For example, a woman came to me asking treatment for prosperity. She did not take much interest

09:22.980 --> 09:29.900
in her household affairs and her home was in great disorder. I said to her, if you wish to be rich,

09:29.900 --> 09:36.500
you must be orderly. All men with great wealth are orderly, and order is heaven's first law.

09:36.980 --> 09:42.280
I added, you will never become rich with a burnt match in the pincushion.

09:43.540 --> 09:47.920
She had a good sense of humor and commenced immediately putting her house in order.

09:48.440 --> 09:54.660
She rearranged furniture, straightened out her bureau drawers, cleaned rugs, and soon made a big

09:54.660 --> 10:02.460
financial demonstration, a gift from a relative. The woman herself became made over and keeps

10:02.460 --> 10:10.220
herself keyed up financially by being ever watchful of the external and expecting prosperity knowing

10:10.220 --> 10:17.840
God is her supply. Many people are in ignorance of the fact that gifts and things are investments

10:17.840 --> 10:23.080
and that hoarding and saving invariably lead to loss.

10:24.160 --> 10:31.780
There is that scattereth and yet increaseth. There is that withholdeth more than is meat,

10:32.260 --> 10:40.320
but it tendeth to poverty. For example, I knew a man who wanted to buy a fur-lined overcoat.

10:40.660 --> 10:47.100
He and his wife went to various shops, but there was none he wanted. He said they were all too

10:47.100 --> 10:55.620
cheap looking. At last he was shown one the salesman said was valued at $1,000, but which the manager

10:55.620 --> 11:03.120
would sell him for $500 as it was late in the season. His financial possessions amounted to

11:03.120 --> 11:10.360
about $700. The reasoning mind would have said, you can't afford to spend nearly all you have on a

11:10.360 --> 11:16.960
coat. But he was very intuitive and never reasoned. He turned to his wife and said,

11:17.560 --> 11:23.800
if I get this coat, I'll make a ton of money. So his wife consented weekly.

11:25.360 --> 11:31.100
About a month later, he received a $10,000 commission. The coat made him feel so rich

11:31.100 --> 11:36.720
it linked him with success and prosperity. Without the coat, he would not have received

11:36.720 --> 11:44.080
the commission. It was an investment paying large dividends. If man ignores these leadings

11:44.080 --> 11:50.620
to spend or to give, the same amount of money will go in an uninteresting or unhappy way.

11:50.960 --> 11:57.740
For example, a woman told me on Thanksgiving Day she informed her family that they could not afford

11:57.740 --> 12:04.880
a Thanksgiving dinner. She had the money, but decided to save it. A few days later, someone

12:04.880 --> 12:10.060
entered her room and took from the bureau drawer the exact amount the dinner would have cost.

12:10.920 --> 12:17.940
The law always stands back of the man who spends fearlessly with wisdom. For example,

12:18.300 --> 12:24.120
one of my students was shopping with her little nephew. The child clamored for a toy which she

12:24.120 --> 12:30.680
told him she could not afford to buy. She realized suddenly that she was seeking lack and not

12:30.680 --> 12:38.020
recognizing God as her supply. So she bought the toy and on her way home, picked up in the street

12:38.020 --> 12:45.280
the exact amount of money she had paid for it. Man's supply is inexhaustible and unfailing when

12:45.280 --> 12:52.300
fully trusted, but faith or trust must precede the demonstration. According to your faith,

12:52.700 --> 13:00.660
be it unto you. Faith is the substance of things hoped for and the evidence of things not seen.

13:01.340 --> 13:08.600
For faith holds the vision steady and the adverse pictures are dissolved and dissipated and

13:08.600 --> 13:17.200
in due season we shall reap if we faint not. Jesus Christ brought the good news, the gospel,

13:17.620 --> 13:23.860
that there was a higher law than the law of karma and that that law transcends the law of karma.

13:23.860 --> 13:31.980
It is the law of grace or forgiveness. It is the law which frees man from the law of cause and

13:31.980 --> 13:42.580
effect, the law of consequence. Under grace, not under law. We are told that on this plain,

13:43.200 --> 13:49.840
man reaps where he has not sown. The gifts of God are simply poured out upon him.

13:50.720 --> 13:56.980
All that the kingdom affords is his. This continued state of bliss

13:56.980 --> 14:05.500
awaits the man who has overcome the race or world thought. In the world thought there is tribulation

14:05.500 --> 14:14.460
but as Jesus Christ said, be of good cheer. I have overcome the world. The world thought is

14:14.460 --> 14:22.060
of sin, sickness and death. He saw their absolute unreality and said sickness and sorrow shall pass

14:22.060 --> 14:30.940
away and death itself, the last enemy, be overcome. We now know from a scientific standpoint that death

14:30.940 --> 14:37.260
could be overcome by stamping the subconscious mind with the conviction of eternal youth and

14:37.260 --> 14:46.540
life. The subconscious, being simply power without direction, carries out orders without questioning.

14:47.800 --> 14:52.360
Working under the direction of the super-conscious, the Christ or God within man,

14:52.940 --> 15:00.540
the resurrection of the body would be accomplished. Man would no longer throw off his body in death.

15:00.540 --> 15:04.700
It would be transformed into the body electric,

15:05.020 --> 15:13.700
sung by Walt Whitman, for Christianity is founded upon the forgiveness of sins and an empty tomb.

